                                </span>
                                <span>Conducted baseline surveys on climate adaptation and local governance</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                                <span
                                    class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs mt-0.5">
                                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                                </span>
                                <span>Partnered with universities for joint research on migration and refugee
                                    issues</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                                <span
                                    class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs mt-0.5">
                                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                                </span>
                                <span>Organized national workshops on disaster risk reduction and sustainable
                                    development</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                                <span
                                    class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs mt-0.5">
                                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                                </span>
                                <span>Developed policy briefs on local governance and public health challenges</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
                                <span
                                    class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs mt-0.5">
                                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
