                                    skills</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-secondary mb-12">Our Core Values</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm text-center reveal">
